@startuml
actor Client
participant LinksController
participant LinkLister

Client -> LinksController: HTTP request to /links with URL parameter
note right of Client: Client requests link extraction

LinksController -> LinkLister: getLinks(url)
note right of LinksController: Extract links from the provided URL

LinksController <-- LinkLister: List<String> (List of extracted links)
Client <-- LinksController: Return JSON response with links
note right of LinksController: Send extracted links to client

alt IOException occurs
    LinkLister --> LinksController: Propagate IOException
    note right of LinkLister: Error handling for URL processing failures
    
    LinksController --> Client: Spring's exception handler processes IOException
    note right of LinksController: Spring converts exception to HTTP error response
end
@enduml